  "name": "Gift of Madness",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "systems/pf1/icons/spells/light-royal-1.jpg",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You tap into the unthinkable void between the stars and cause a single living creature within 30 feet to become confused for 1 round. A successful Will save negates the effect. This is a mind-affecting compulsion effect.</p>\n<p>At 7th level, the confusion lasts for a number of rounds equal to your oracle level.</p>\n<p>You can use this ability a number of times per day equal to 3 + your Charisma modifier.</p>"
